# Styling Rules for Cursor
- Use Tailwind CSS for all styling (no inline CSS or other frameworks).
- Color scheme: navy (`#002C51`), white (`#FFFFFF`), red (`#F11A20`).
- Typography: Inter (body), Rubik (headings).
- Mobile-first design with Tailwind breakpoints (e.g., `sm:`, `md:`).



- Hover effects: Use red accents (e.g., `hover:border-red-600`).